description: A woman director is hired to finish the season of "Bikini Squad", a popular TV series about California beach lifeguards. A more than obvious lack of talent and basic intelligence among the crew make her contemplate leaving the set.
name: Bikini Squad

review.name: Favorite Trash Movies
review.reviewBody:
Bikini Squad is simply great trash - this is a category of it's own with it's own rules: some people LOVE it, others hate it and will never understand why other people may love this kind of ยง$%&#* ;-)

This is in my Top.10 of all-time trash'n'fun for sure - it has everything-a-trash-movie-needs: sexy actors, gifted for trash, well-known slapstick gags, senseless violence, awful dialogs, a storyline you may guess 1 minute after watching this movie first time.

take-a-seat on your couch and open the popcorn bag: we're crossing the borderline of good taste.

aw - i love it. <3
